    <list default="true" id="d636adb8-ceea-4d1b-886f-a5eba9ec35ca" name="Changes" comment="OreCzml V2.0 changes :&#10;- Name reworked : OreCZML -&gt; OreCzml&#10;- Repository root renamed : org.example -&gt; org.orekit.czml&#10;- JavaDoc of all classes added.&#10;- Renamed : CZMLFile -&gt; CzmlFile.&#10;- REWORK : renamed generateCZML() -&gt; writeCZMLBlock() . The writeCZMLBlocks function will be called directly in the CZMLFile.java instead of each time a primary object is added.&#10;- REWORK : The user only need to build a CzmlFile now, build the objects and call the CzmlFile.write() function.&#10;- Add the AbstractPrimaryObject class to add a layer and a common ground for each PrimaryObject.&#10;- Added scr/tutorial for future tutorials added here, for the moment, the OreCzml main is there for tests.&#10;- Header object can no longer be built with a propagator.&#10;- Renamed CZMLGroundStation -&gt; CzmlGroundStation&#10;- CzmlGroundStation can no longer be built with an Orekit groundStation.&#10;- A directory CzmlEnum has been created for each enum used.">
